articles.title: Cody Simpson’s sister Alli seriously injured in New Year’s Eve swimming pool accident - PerthNow
articles.description: Reality star Alli Simpson says she is grateful to survive a nightmare accident in a swimming pool. And to make matters worse, she also has COVID-19.
articles.content:
